    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If authentication fails 10 times, Gdata servers force a CAPTCHA challenge to ensure that the client is a legitimate human and not a bot.</p>

<p>Currently the ClientLogin mechanism for Zend_Gdata does not support CAPTCHA response.</p>

